## Bug Report Template

When a bug is found, Claude Code must create a file in `docs/bugs/BUG-{N}.md`:

```markdown
## BUG-{N}: {Short Title}

**Severity:** Critical | High | Medium | Low
**Component:** Ingestion | Query Engine | API | Frontend | Security
**Phase:** 1 | 2 | 3...

### Steps to Reproduce
1. ...
2. ...

### Actual Result
{What happened}

### Expected Result
{What should have happened}

### Data / Payload
```json
{ ... }
```

### Regression Test
{Test case to add to the test suite to prevent recurrence}

**Status:** Open | In Progress | Fixed | Verified
```

